lead_paragraph: Wallabies great George Smith will continue playing top class rugby until at least the age of 38 after signing a two-year deal to return to Australia with the Queensland Reds Super Rugby team on Friday.

headline.print_headline: Evergreen Smith to Return to Australia With Reds
